=========================================================
COLLEGE MANAGEMENT SYSTEM (CMS)
Project Blueprint & Functional Requirements
=========================================================

Project Name:
College Management System (CMS)

Project Type:
Single College Management System

Architecture:
Backend: Django + Django REST Framework
Database: PostgreSQL
Authentication: JWT
Authorization: RBAC (Role-Based Access Control)
Frontend: React + TypeScript
Storage: Local Storage / AWS S3 (Future)
Deployment: Docker + Nginx + Gunicorn

---------------------------------------------------------
PROJECT OVERVIEW
---------------------------------------------------------

The College Management System (CMS) is a centralized platform
designed to manage academic, administrative, examination,
attendance, and financial operations of a college.

The system aims to digitize and automate day-to-day activities
performed by administrators, teachers, accountants, and students.

The platform will provide separate portals for different users
with role-based access and permissions.

---------------------------------------------------------
