=========================================================
USER JOURNEYS
=========================================================

---------------------------------------------------------
1. STUDENT JOURNEY
---------------------------------------------------------

Student Registration
    ↓
Admission Approval
    ↓
Fee Payment
    ↓
Student Account Creation
    ↓
Student Enrollment
    ↓
Class Participation
    ↓
Attendance Tracking
    ↓
Examinations
    ↓
Result Publication
    ↓
Semester Completion
    ↓
Next Semester Enrollment

Student can:

- Login to Portal
- View Dashboard
- View Profile
- Download Student ID
- View Attendance
- View Results
- View GPA / CGPA
- View Fee Information
- View Payment History
- View Notifications
- Access Academic Records

---------------------------------------------------------
2. TEACHER JOURNEY
---------------------------------------------------------

Faculty Profile Creation
    ↓
Subject Assignment
    ↓
Section Assignment
    ↓
Teacher Account Creation
    ↓
Class Management
    ↓
Attendance Marking
    ↓
Marks Entry
    ↓
Result Processing

Teacher can:

- Login to Portal
- View Dashboard
- View Assigned Subjects
- View Assigned Sections
- Take Attendance
- Update Attendance
- Enter Exam Marks
- View Student Lists
- Apply Leave
- View Notifications

---------------------------------------------------------
3. ACCOUNTANT JOURNEY
---------------------------------------------------------

Fee Structure Setup
    ↓
Student Fee Assignment
    ↓
Fee Collection
    ↓
Receipt Generation
    ↓
Financial Reporting

Accountant can:

- Login to Portal
- View Dashboard
- Search Students
- Collect Fees
- Generate Receipts
- View Payment History
- Manage Fee Structures
- View Due Reports
- Generate Financial Reports

---------------------------------------------------------
4. ADMIN JOURNEY
---------------------------------------------------------

Academic Setup
    ↓
Program Creation
    ↓
Semester Creation
    ↓
Subject Creation
    ↓
Section Creation
    ↓
Faculty Assignment
    ↓
Student Admission
    ↓
Fee Configuration
    ↓
Attendance Monitoring
    ↓
Exam Management
    ↓
Result Publication
    ↓
Reporting & Analytics

Admin can:

- Manage Students
- Manage Faculty
- Manage Academic Structure
- Manage Attendance
- Manage Examinations
- Publish Results
- Configure Fees
- Create Notifications
